manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Olay Total Effects fights the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles with a proven vitamin complex. Total Effects cleansers, eye/specialty treatments, and moisturizers were designed to fight 7 signs of aging. Experience beautiful, healthier-looking skin every day with Olay Total Effects. Product Description Olay Total Effects 7-IN-1 Fragrance Free Anti-Aging Moisturizer with SPF 15 is reformulated with 40% more vitamins for an effortless look. This formula with its VitaNiacin Complex fights the 7 signs of aging with vitamin B3. The 7-in-1 formula combines humectants and skin conditioners to help keep skin hydrated. Plus, its vitamins and antioxidants hydrate to help reduce the look of age spots, minimize the appearance of pores, and reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. This fragrance-free facial moisturizer with SPF 15 nourishes with hydration to visibly reduce signs of aging for younger-looking skin. Fights the 7 signs of aging with hydration to reduce the look of fine lines and wrinkles Combines powerful hydration with 40% more vitamins Broad Spectrum SPF 15 protects from harmful UVA/UVB rays

7 Benefits In One 1. Visibly smoothes fine lines and wrinkles 2. Evens skin tone appearance 3. Enhances brightness 4. Minimizes the look of pores 5. Visibly reduces age spots 6. Restores firmness 7. Replenishes moisture Formulated with SolaSheer Technology, this moisturizer protects skin against harmful UVA/UVB rays with Broad Spectrum SPF 15. Fight the #1 cause of premature skin aging*- the sun, with Olay’s Total Effects 7-in-1 Fragrance Free Anti-Aging Moisturizer with SPF 15. *when used as directed with other skin protection measures Olay Total Effects 7-in-1 Fragrance Free Anti-Aging Moisturizer with SPF 15 is just one of many beneficial steps you can take to fight the 7 signs of aging and improve your skin’s appearance. Customize your own regimen with vitamin-rich formulas of cleansers, serums, eye/specialty treatments to target specific skincare concerns, and moisturizers. 1. Cleanser: Total Effects Nourishing Cream Cleanser 2. Eye Treatment: Total Effects Anti-Aging Eye Treatment 3. Day Moisturizer: Total Effects 7-in-1 Fragrance-Free Anti-Aging Moisturizer with SPF 15 Night Moisturizer: Total Effects 7-in-1 Fragrance-Free Anti-Aging Moisturizer

Q: How does Olay Total Effects Anti-Aging Fragrance Free Moisturizer with SPF 15 fit into my current regimen? A: Olay Total Effects Anti-Aging Fragrance Free Moisturizer with SPF 15 is the third step of our suggested regimen: Moisturizer. After cleansing and treating skin, apply this moisturizer to rehydrate and replenish your skin with our VitaNiacin Complex. Q: What’s a VitaNiacin Complex? A: This formula contains a VitaNiacin complex, with Vitamins C&E, that exfoliates to enhance skin’s natural self-renewal process for healthier-looking skin in 4 weeks. Q: How often can I use Olay Anti-Aging Fragrance Free Moisturizer with SPF 15? A: It is recommended to be applied in the morning to provide sun protection. Reapply every two hours to help prevent sunburn.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars ✨ "Skin Savior: Olay Total Effects 7-in-1 Moisturizer - Our Daily Essential!" ✨
reviews.reviewText: The Olay Total Effects 7-in-1 Moisturizer is our absolute go-to for amazing skin! Both my hubby and I have been using this magical stuff religiously for the past six years. It's like our secret weapon for a fresh and youthful face every single day. 🌟🌼 Top 5 Takeaways 🌼1️⃣ All-in-One Wonder: This moisturizer does it all! It tackles fine lines, wrinkles, and gives our skin a seriously awesome boost. It's like having seven skincare products rolled into one bottle - it's that good!2️⃣ No Nasty Fragrance: We're all about that fragrance-free life! This moisturizer keeps it simple and gentle on the nose. No overwhelming scents, just pure goodness that our skin craves.3️⃣ Bye-Bye Sun Worries: With SPF 15, it's got our backs (and our faces!) covered. It helps shield our skin from the sun's harmful rays and keeps those pesky signs of aging at bay. Gotta love a moisturizer that multitasks!4️⃣ Light and Breezy: We love how this moisturizer sinks right in without feeling heavy or greasy. It's like a refreshing drink for our skin, leaving it soft, smooth, and ready to take on the day. No pore-clogging worries either!5️⃣ Age-Defying Results: It's the real deal, folks! Our skin has seriously improved since we started using this moisturizer. It's firmer, more even-toned, and just plain healthier-looking. It's like a mini time machine for our faces!⭐ Pros ⭐✅ Does the work of multiple skincare products.✅ No overpowering fragrance, just freshness.✅ Sun protection with SPF 15 - sunscreen, sorted!✅ Lightweight, non-greasy, and ready to go.✅ Gives real results, making us look and feel awesome.⛔ Cons ⛔❌ SPF 15 might not be enough for intense sun exposure.❌ Limited size options - a bigger bottle would be great!🌸 To sum it up, the Olay Total Effects 7-in-1 Moisturizer is our skincare superhero. It's like a secret weapon against aging, giving us that fresh-faced glow we love. This stuff is seriously the bomb! So, if you're after amazing skin that's totally fuss-free, give this moisturizer a shot. You won't regret it! 🌸

reviews.reviewTitle: I am 28 years old and this is my favorite face cream
reviews.reviewText: I am 28 years old and this is my favorite face cream! I have been using off and on for 3 years now - Especially when i have an event coming up in a couple weeks i really get in to it ;) It states it can make your skin look up to 10 years younger within 4 weeks. Some might say i am 'too young' to be using anti-aging product but i feel like this gives me a head start. I usually apply about twice a day - once before bed and once out of shower in the morning - does not feel heavy or greasy.. my skin loves it! Also i saved a few bucks than if i would have purchased in store and it was delivered to my door so cant go wrong there! I wouldn't recommend the one with SPF though as that is mostly what it is. Original is best although i use fragrance free because my skin is sensitive to perfumes. Haven't tried the touch of sun one and don't really feel inclined to either.. when you find something you like you tend to want to stick to it!
